@startuml
title InsightsRadar v1 - ArticlesTileView Infinite Scroll

actor User
participant "Web App\nArticlesTileView" as Web
participant "Worker API\nGET /api/articles" as API
database "D1 Metadata DB" as D1

User -> Web: open /
Web -> API: GET /api/articles?limit=20
API -> D1: query processed tiles\nORDER BY published_at DESC, canonical_url DESC
D1 --> API: rows + hasMore
API --> Web: items + nextCursor
Web -> Web: render 2-col desktop / 1-col mobile

loop while sentinel intersects and nextCursor != null
  Web -> API: GET /api/articles?cursor=<opaque>&limit=20
  API -> D1: cursor tuple pagination
  D1 --> API: next rows
  API --> Web: append items + nextCursor
end

alt request error
  API --> Web: non-2xx response
  Web -> Web: show error + retry CTA
  User -> Web: click Retry
  Web -> API: repeat last page request
end

@enduml
